    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi, thanks a lot!\n\nWe did not think of that use case indeed, what you would need to use here is the unconnected component (RefinementList) I guess. We do not expose it today.\n\nI am not comfortable with your patch right now, I feel like we are patching something that is not meant to be used this way. I guess we could just expose the non-connected components for you to reuse like you just did.\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
