    "body": "@Kikobeats We are not yet sure on the best way on how to do that and so will hold on this feature for now. You can definitely reimplement your own RefinementList instead of tryin to reuse the `<RefinementList/>` here by using the connector API.\n\nSorry this is not the best solution we think right now but we don't want to go too fast and keep some space for API additions by getting more feedback and ideas. Thanks a lot for contribution though.\n",
