    "body": "Hmm, I fixed the problem with the imports doing:\n\n``` jsx\nimport React, {PropTypes, Component} from 'react';\nimport pick from 'lodash/pick';\nimport themeable from 'react-instantsearch/src/core/themeable';\nimport translatable from 'react-instantsearch/src/core/translatable';\nimport List from 'react-instantsearch/src/components/List';\n\nconst theme = {\n  root:  {},\n  item:  {},\n  itemSelected:  {},\n  itemLabel:  {},\n  itemCount:  {},\n  showMore:  {},\n  showMoreDisabled:  {},\n  itemLabelSelected:  {},\n  itemCountSelected:  {},\n  itemCheckbox: {},\n  itemCheckboxSelected: {}\n}\n```\n\nnew problem:\n\n```\nwarning.js:36 Warning: Failed prop type: Required prop `refine` was not specified in `RefinementList`.\n```\n\nNow I don't know what do 🎃 \n",
