    "body": "That's very hacky eheh indeed since none of those are official API entries and might just be removed.\n\nI would go for reimplementing your own small refinement list, since it should be less code than what you did.\n\nI understand that we are not very explicit on the default widgets goals. Basically as soon as you hit a feature wall (can't do X), you need to use connectors.\n\nThe Panel question is currently a pain we need to solve\n",
